                            <comment id="14660152" author="aivanov" created="Mon, 25 Mar 2024 10:07:21 -0700"  >This is a regression from &lt;a href=&quot;https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8146319&quot; title=&quot;JEditorPane function setPage leaves a file lock&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;JDK-8146319&quot;&gt;&lt;strike&gt;JDK-8146319&lt;/strike&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. JEditorPane catches ChangedCharSetException but it cannot reset the InputStream because the stream is closed by try-with-resources. It means in.reset() [1] throws IOException with the message &amp;quot;Stream closed&amp;quot;.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
[1] &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/openjdk/jdk/blob/78d1b9046830198cd61c505f04f245a430878a5b/src/java.desktop/share/classes/javax/swing/JEditorPane.java#L632-L634&quot;&gt;https://github.com/openjdk/jdk/blob/78d1b9046830198cd61c505f04f245a430878a5b/src/java.desktop/share/classes/javax/swing/JEditorPane.java#L632-L634&lt;/a&gt;</comment>
